Clustering - all samples after QC

suppressMessages(library(Seurat))
suppressMessages(library(ggplot2))
suppressMessages(library(clustree))
srt <- readRDS("/mnt/nmorais-nfs/marta/pB_joana/pC_data/srt-mono-macs-from-raw-bec.rds")
srt <- FindNeighbors(srt, 
                     reduction = "pca", 
                     dims = seq_len(30),
                     compute.SNN = TRUE)
## Computing nearest neighbor graph
## Computing SNN
for (r in (res <- seq(0.1, 2, 0.1)))
    srt <- FindClusters(srt, 
                        resolution = r, 
                        random.seed = 1234,
                        verbose = FALSE)
names(srt@meta.data)
##  [1] "orig.ident"      "nCount_RNA"      "nFeature_RNA"    "sample"         
##  [5] "lane"            "sorting_day"     "cell_type"       "RNA_snn_res.0.1"
##  [9] "seurat_clusters" "RNA_snn_res.0.2" "RNA_snn_res.0.3" "RNA_snn_res.0.4"
## [13] "RNA_snn_res.0.5" "RNA_snn_res.0.6" "RNA_snn_res.0.7" "RNA_snn_res.0.8"
## [17] "RNA_snn_res.0.9" "RNA_snn_res.1"   "RNA_snn_res.1.1" "RNA_snn_res.1.2"
## [21] "RNA_snn_res.1.3" "RNA_snn_res.1.4" "RNA_snn_res.1.5" "RNA_snn_res.1.6"
## [25] "RNA_snn_res.1.7" "RNA_snn_res.1.8" "RNA_snn_res.1.9" "RNA_snn_res.2"
df_clusters <- as.data.frame(srt@meta.data[6:28])
df_clusters$seurat_clusters <- NULL
df_clusters
clustree(df_clusters[,1:10], 
         prefix = "RNA_snn_res.") +
  theme(text = element_text(size=20))

saveRDS(srt,"/mnt/nmorais-nfs/marta/pB_joana/pC_data/srt-mono-macs-from-raw-bec.rds")
